@startuml EmiyaOJ-Cloud-DFD-Level1

' ============================================================
' EmiyaOJ-Cloud 数据流图 (DFD) — Level 1 系统级
' ============================================================

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title **EmiyaOJ-Cloud — Level 1 系统级数据流图**

' --- 外部实体 ---
rectangle "用户" as User_E1
rectangle "管理员" as Admin_E1
rectangle "阿里云审核 API" as Aliyun_E1
rectangle "AI 大模型" as LLM_E1

' --- 处理过程 ---
component "**P1**\n认证授权" as P1_Auth #E3F2FD
component "**P2**\n题目/竞赛管理" as P2_Problem #E8F5E9
component "**P3**\n代码判题" as P3_Judge #FFF9C4
component "**P4**\n博客社区" as P4_Blog #F3E5F5
component "**P5**\nAI 聊天" as P5_Chat #E0F7FA
component "**P6**\n内容审核" as P6_Moderation #FFECB3

' --- 数据存储 ---
database "**D1**\nMySQL\n(emiya_oj_*)" as D1_MySQL
database "**D2**\nRedis\n(Token白名单)" as D2_Redis
database "**D3**\nRabbitMQ\n(审核消息队列)" as D3_MQ
database "**D4**\nMinIO\n(图片对象存储)" as D4_MinIO
database "**D5**\nNacos\n(服务注册)" as D5_Nacos

' ============================================
' 数据流定义
' ============================================

' ---- 用户 → P1 认证 ----
User_E1 -[#0000FF]down-> P1_Auth : **1.1** 登录请求\n(username, password)

' ---- P1 → D1/D2 ----
P1_Auth -[#006400]right-> D1_MySQL : **1.2** 查询用户/角色/权限
P1_Auth -[#FF4500]right-> D2_Redis : **1.3** 写入 Token 白名单\nSET token_{userId}

' ---- P1 → 用户 ----
P1_Auth -[#0000FF]up-> User_E1 : **1.4** JWT Token + 用户信息

' ---- 用户 → P2 题目/竞赛 ----
User_E1 -[#0000FF]down-> P2_Problem : **2.1** 浏览题目/竞赛/题单/排名

' ---- P2 → D1 ----
P2_Problem -[#006400]left-> D1_MySQL : **2.2** 题目CRUD\n**2.3** 竞赛·题单·语言·标签

' ---- P2 → 用户 ----
P2_Problem -[#0000FF]up-> User_E1 : **2.4** 题目列表/详情\n竞赛信息/排名

' ---- 管理员 → P2 ----
Admin_E1 -[#8B4513]down-> P2_Problem : **2.5** 管理题目/用例/竞赛/题单

' ---- 用户 → P3 判题 ----
User_E1 -[#0000FF]down-> P3_Judge : **3.1** 提交代码\n(problemId, languageId, code)

' ---- P3 → P2 (Feign) ----
P3_Judge -[#555555]left-> P2_Problem : **3.2** 获取题目/测试用例/语言配置

' ---- P3 → D1 ----
P3_Judge -[#006400]right-> D1_MySQL : **3.3** 写入提交记录\n**3.4** 更新判题结果

' ---- P3 → Go-Judge ----
P3_Judge -[#DC143C]right-> P3_Judge : **3.5** HTTP → Go-Judge\n编译 & 运行 (沙箱)

' ---- P3 → 用户 ----
P3_Judge -[#0000FF]up-> User_E1 : **3.6** 判题结果\n(AC/WA/TLE/CE...)

' ---- 用户 → P4 博客 ----
User_E1 -[#0000FF]down-> P4_Blog : **4.1** 发博客/评论/点赞/收藏

' ---- P4 → D4 (MinIO) ----
P4_Blog -[#FF69B4]right-> D4_MinIO : **4.2** 上传/下载图片

' ---- P4 → D3 (MQ) ----
P4_Blog -[#FF8C00]right-> D3_MQ : **4.3** 发布审核任务

' ---- P4 → D1 ----
P4_Blog -[#006400]left-> D1_MySQL : **4.4** 博客/评论/标签CRUD

' ---- P4 → 用户 ----
P4_Blog -[#0000FF]up-> User_E1 : **4.5** 博客列表/详情/评论

' ---- D3 → P6 审核 ----
D3_MQ -[#FF8C00]down-> P6_Moderation : **6.1** 消费审核任务\n(@RabbitListener)

' ---- P6 → 阿里云 ----
P6_Moderation -[#DC143C]right-> Aliyun_E1 : **6.2** ScanText 请求

' ---- 阿里云 → P6 ----
Aliyun_E1 -[#DC143C]left-> P6_Moderation : **6.3** 审核结果

' ---- P6 → P4 (Feign 回调) ----
P6_Moderation -[#555555]left-> P4_Blog : **6.4** 回写审核结果\n(POST /blog/internal/...)

' ---- 管理员 → P4 ----
Admin_E1 -[#8B4513]down-> P4_Blog : **4.6** 人工审核操作

' ---- 管理员 → P1 ----
Admin_E1 -[#8B4513]down-> P1_Auth : **1.5** 用户/角色/权限管理

' ---- 用户 → P5 ----
User_E1 -[#0000FF]down-> P5_Chat : **5.1** AI对话消息

' ---- P5 → LLM ----
P5_Chat -[#9370DB]right-> LLM_E1 : **5.2** Chat API 调用

' ---- LLM → P5 ----
LLM_E1 -[#9370DB]left-> P5_Chat : **5.3** AI 回复

' ---- P5 → 用户 ----
P5_Chat -[#0000FF]up-> User_E1 : **5.4** AI 回复文本

' ---- 网关认证流 (所有请求经过 P1) ----
note top of P1_Auth
  **Gateway (8080) 全局认证**
  ────────────────────────
  所有用户/管理员请求必须
  经过 Gateway → AuthGlobalFilter:
  ① JWT 解析 (HMAC-SHA256)
  ② Redis 白名单验证
  ③ 注入请求头:
     X-User-Id
     X-User-Name
     X-User-Roles
  ④ 白名单路径直接放行
end note

note bottom of P3_Judge
  **Go-Judge 沙箱交互**
  ─────────────────────
  JudgeService → GoJudgeService
    · compile(code, lang) → 编译
    · run(lang, fileIds, case) → 运行
  POST http://go-judge:5050/run
  返回: status, time, memory, files
end note

note bottom of D1_MySQL
  **MySQL 8.0.31 数据库**
  ──────────────────────
  · emiya_oj_auth
    User, Role, Permission,
    UserRole, RolePermission
  · emiya_oj_problem
    Problem, TestCase, Language,
    Tag, ProblemTag, Contest,
    ContestProblem, ContestRegistration
  · emiya_oj_judge
    Submission, SubmissionResult,
    MessageEvent
  · emiya_oj_blog
    Blog, BlogComment, BlogStar,
    BlogTag, BlogPicture, UserBlog
end note

@enduml

' ================================================================

@startuml EmiyaOJ-Cloud-DFD-Level2-P1

' ============================================================
' EmiyaOJ-Cloud 数据流图 — Level 2: P1 认证授权
' ============================================================

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title **EmiyaOJ-Cloud — Level 2: P1 认证授权数据流图**

rectangle "用户" as User_E2a

component "**P1.1**\n登录认证" as P11_Login #E3F2FD
component "**P1.2**\nToken 管理" as P12_Token #E3F2FD
component "**P1.3**\n网关鉴权过滤" as P13_Gateway #E3F2FD
component "**P1.4**\n用户CRUD" as P14_User #E3F2FD
component "**P1.5**\n角色权限管理" as P15_Role #E3F2FD

database "**D1.1**\nuser 表" as D11_User
database "**D1.2**\nrole·permission 表" as D12_Role
database "**D1.3**\nuser_role·role_permission 表" as D13_Rel
database "**D2**\nRedis Token白名单" as D2_Redis2

' 登录流程
User_E2a -[#0000FF]down-> P11_Login : username, password
P11_Login -[#006400]right-> D11_User : 查询用户
P11_Login -[#006400]right-> D13_Rel : 查询角色·权限
P11_Login -[#555555]down-> P12_Token : 签发Token请求
P12_Token -[#FF4500]right-> D2_Redis2 : SET token_{userId}
P11_Login -[#0000FF]up-> User_E2a : JWT Token + 用户信息

' 网关鉴权
User_E2a -[#0000FF]down-> P13_Gateway : 业务请求 + Bearer Token
P13_Gateway -[#FF4500]left-> D2_Redis2 : EXISTS token_{userId}
P13_Gateway -[#555555]down-> P12_Token : 解析 JWT
P13_Gateway -[#555555]right-> P13_Gateway : 注入 X-User-Id\nX-User-Name\nX-User-Roles

' 用户管理
P14_User -[#006400]right-> D11_User : CRUD 用户
P15_Role -[#006400]right-> D12_Role : CRUD 角色·权限
P15_Role -[#006400]right-> D13_Rel : 维护关联关系

' 登出
P12_Token -[#FF4500]left-> D2_Redis2 : DEL token_{userId}

note right of P13_Gateway
  **AuthGlobalFilter**
  ────────────────
  ① 白名单路径放行
  ② 提取 Bearer Token
  ③ JwtUtil.parseJWT()
  ④ Redis 白名单验证
  ⑤ 注入请求头
  Order = -100
end note

@enduml

' ================================================================

@startuml EmiyaOJ-Cloud-DFD-Level2-P3

' ============================================================
' EmiyaOJ-Cloud 数据流图 — Level 2: P3 代码判题
' ============================================================

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title **EmiyaOJ-Cloud — Level 2: P3 代码判题数据流图**

rectangle "用户" as User_E2b

component "**P3.1**\n提交创建" as P31_Submit #FFF9C4
component "**P3.2**\n异步判题执行" as P32_JudgeExec #FFF9C4
component "**P3.3**\nGo-Judge 交互" as P33_GoJudge #FFF9C4
component "**P3.4**\n结果汇总计算" as P34_Result #FFF9C4
component "**P3.5**\n提交查询" as P35_Query #FFF9C4

component "**P2.x**\nProblem Service\n(Feign 调用)" as P2x_Feign #E8F5E9

database "**D1.4**\nsubmission 表" as D14_Sub
database "**D1.5**\nsubmission_result 表" as D15_Result
database "**D1.6**\nmessage_event 表" as D16_Msg

' 提交流程
User_E2b -[#0000FF]down-> P31_Submit : **S1** problemId, languageId, code
P31_Submit -[#006400]right-> D14_Sub : **S2** INSERT\n(status=0 Pending)
P31_Submit -[#555555]down-> P32_JudgeExec : **S3** @Async 触发
P31_Submit -[#0000FF]up-> User_E2b : **S4** 返回 submissionId\n(status=Pending)

' 判题执行流程
P32_JudgeExec -[#555555]left-> P2x_Feign : **S5** GET /problem/{id}\n**S6** GET /test-case/problem/{id}\n**S7** GET /language/{id}
P2x_Feign -[#555555]right-> P32_JudgeExec : **S8** 题目·测试用例·语言配置
P32_JudgeExec -[#006400]right-> D14_Sub : **S9** UPDATE status=1 Judging
P32_JudgeExec -[#555555]down-> P33_GoJudge : **S10** compile(code, lang)

' Go-Judge 交互
P33_GoJudge -[#DC143C]right-> P33_GoJudge : **S11** HTTP POST /run\n(编译/运行)

' 逐用例循环
P33_GoJudge -[#555555]up-> P32_JudgeExec : **S12** 编译结果/文件ID

note right of P32_JudgeExec
  **逐用例循环**
  ─────────────
  for each TestCase:
    run(code, fileIds, input)
    → 获取实际输出
    → 对比预期输出
    → 收集时间/内存/状态
end note

P32_JudgeExec -[#555555]down-> P34_Result : **S13** 逐用例结果

' 结果汇总
P34_Result -[#006400]right-> D15_Result : **S14** INSERT 逐用例记录
P34_Result -[#006400]up-> D14_Sub : **S15** UPDATE 最终状态\n(AC/WA/TLE/MLE/CE/RE/PA)
P34_Result -[#006400]right-> D16_Msg : **S16** 本地消息表\n(分布式事务)

' 查询流程
User_E2b -[#0000FF]down-> P35_Query : **S17** GET /submission/{id}\nGET /submission/my
P35_Query -[#006400]left-> D14_Sub : **S18** SELECT
P35_Query -[#006400]left-> D15_Result : **S19** SELECT 逐用例
P35_Query -[#0000FF]up-> User_E2b : **S20** 提交详情+逐用例结果

note bottom of P32_JudgeExec
  **@Async 异步执行**
  ───────────────────
  · 不阻塞提交接口响应
  · 用户立即获得 submissionId
  · 轮询 GET /submission/{id} 获取结果
  · 分布式事务: 本地消息表 + 重试
end note

@enduml

' ================================================================

@startuml EmiyaOJ-Cloud-DFD-Level2-P4P6

' ============================================================
' EmiyaOJ-Cloud 数据流图 — Level 2: P4/P6 博客审核
' ============================================================

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title **EmiyaOJ-Cloud — Level 2: P4/P6 博客发布与内容审核数据流图**

rectangle "用户" as User_E2c
rectangle "管理员" as Admin_E2c

component "**P4.1**\n博客/题解发布" as P41_Blog #F3E5F5
component "**P4.2**\n评论互动" as P42_Comment #F3E5F5
component "**P4.3**\n点赞/收藏" as P43_Like #F3E5F5
component "**P4.4**\n图片上传" as P44_Image #F3E5F5
component "**P4.5**\n审核任务投递" as P45_Publish #F3E5F5

component "**P6.1**\n审核任务消费" as P61_Consume #FFECB3
component "**P6.2**\n阿里云 ScanText" as P62_ScanText #FFECB3
component "**P6.3**\n审核结果回写" as P63_Callback #FFECB3
component "**P4.6**\n人工审核" as P46_Manual #F3E5F5

database "**D1.7**\nblog 表\n(audit_status 审核状态)" as D17_Blog
database "**D1.8**\nblog_comment 表" as D18_Comment
database "**D1.9**\nblog_like·blog_star 表" as D19_Like
database "**D3**\nRabbitMQ\n(emiyaoj.moderation.*)" as D3_MQ2
database "**D4**\nMinIO\n(博客图片)" as D4_MinIO2

rectangle "阿里云\n内容审核 API" as Aliyun_E2c

' --- 博客发布 ---
User_E2c -[#0000FF]down-> P41_Blog : **B1** title, content, tagIds
P41_Blog -[#006400]right-> D17_Blog : **B2** INSERT\n(auditStatus=0 PENDING)
P41_Blog -[#555555]down-> P45_Publish : **B3** 触发审核
P41_Blog -[#0000FF]up-> User_E2c : **B4** 博客ID (待审核)

' --- 评论 ---
User_E2c -[#0000FF]down-> P42_Comment : **B5** blogId, content
P42_Comment -[#006400]right-> D18_Comment : **B6** INSERT (auditStatus=0)
P42_Comment -[#555555]down-> P45_Publish : **B7** 触发审核

' --- 图片上传 ---
User_E2c -[#0000FF]down-> P44_Image : **B8** 图片文件
P44_Image -[#FF69B4]right-> D4_MinIO2 : **B9** PUT 图片
D4_MinIO2 -[#FF69B4]left-> P44_Image : **B10** 图片 URL
P44_Image -[#0000FF]up-> User_E2c : **B11** 图片 URL

' --- 点赞/收藏 ---
User_E2c -[#0000FF]down-> P43_Like : **B12** 点赞/收藏/取消
P43_Like -[#006400]right-> D19_Like : **B13** INSERT/DELETE
P43_Like -[#006400]right-> D17_Blog : **B14** 触发器更新统计

' --- 审核任务队列 ---
P45_Publish -[#FF8C00]right-> D3_MQ2 : **B15** publish\n(routingKey + payload)

' --- 审核消费 ---
D3_MQ2 -[#FF8C00]down-> P61_Consume : **B16** @RabbitListener\n消费消息
P61_Consume -[#555555]down-> P62_ScanText : **B17** 解析消息

' --- 调用阿里云 ---
P62_ScanText -[#DC143C]right-> Aliyun_E2c : **B18** ScanText\n(待审核文本)
Aliyun_E2c -[#DC143C]left-> P62_ScanText : **B19** suggestion + labels

' --- 回写 ---
P62_ScanText -[#555555]down-> P63_Callback : **B20** 审核结果
P63_Callback -[#555555]left-> P41_Blog : **B21** Feign 回调\nPOST /blog/internal/moderation/result\n(X-Moderation-Token)
P41_Blog -[#006400]left-> D17_Blog : **B22** UPDATE audit_status\n(APPROVED/REJECTED/MANUAL_REVIEW)
P63_Callback -[#555555]left-> P42_Comment : **B23** Feign 回调 (评论)
P42_Comment -[#006400]left-> D18_Comment : **B24** UPDATE audit_status

' --- 人工审核 ---
Admin_E2c -[#8B4513]down-> P46_Manual : **B25** PUT /blog/moderation/.../status
P46_Manual -[#006400]right-> D17_Blog : **B26** UPDATE audit_status
P46_Manual -[#006400]right-> D18_Comment : **B27** UPDATE audit_status

note bottom of D3_MQ2
  **审核消息格式**
  ──────────────
  Exchange: emiyaoj.moderation.exchange
  Type: Topic
  RoutingKey:
    moderation.blog
    moderation.comment
  Payload (JSON):
    { taskId, targetType, targetId,
      userId, content }
end note

note right of P62_ScanText
  **阿里云 ScanText API**
  ───────────────────────
  返回 suggestion:
  · pass → auditStatus=1 (APPROVED)
  · review → auditStatus=3 (人工复核)
  · block → auditStatus=2 (REJECTED)
  命中标签: abuse, politics,
            violence, spam...
end note

@enduml

